stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> PermissionDenied : permission denied
    [*] --> AwaitingFCMToken : permission granted

    PermissionDenied --> AwaitingFCMToken : user enables in OS settings

    AwaitingFCMToken --> Unregistered : FCM token received

    Unregistered --> Ready : online and registerToken() succeeds
    Unregistered --> Unregistered : offline or registerToken() fails (retry on reconnect or foreground)

    Ready --> Ready : update succeeds or rolls back if offline
